  "solution": [
    "## Solutions to Vector Product Exercises",
    "",
    "### Exercise 1: Computing Cross Product - Determinant Method",
    "",
    "**a)** $\\vec{a} \\times \\vec{b} = \\begin{vmatrix} \\hat{i} & \\hat{j} & \\hat{k} \\\\ 2 & 3 & 1 \\\\ 1 & 0 & 4 \\end{vmatrix} = \\hat{i}(3\\times4 - 1\\times0) - \\hat{j}(2\\times4 - 1\\times1) + \\hat{k}(2\\times0 - 3\\times1) = 12\\hat{i} - 7\\hat{j} - 3\\hat{k}$",
    "",
    "**b)** $\\vec{c} \\times \\vec{d} = \\begin{vmatrix} \\hat{i} & \\hat{j} & \\hat{k} \\\\ 1 & 2 & 3 \\\\ 4 & 5 & 6 \\end{vmatrix} = \\hat{i}(2\\times6 - 3\\times5) - \\hat{j}(1\\times6 - 3\\times4) + \\hat{k}(1\\times5 - 2\\times4) = (12-15)\\hat{i} - (6-12)\\hat{j} + (5-8)\\hat{k} = -3\\hat{i} + 6\\hat{j} - 3\\hat{k}$",
    "",
    "**c)** $\\vec{p} \\times \\vec{q} = \\begin{vmatrix} \\hat{i} & \\hat{j} & \\hat{k} \\\\ -1 & 2 & 0 \\\\ 3 & 1 & -2 \\end{vmatrix} = \\hat{i}(2\\times(-2) - 0\\times1) - \\hat{j}(-1\\times(-2) - 0\\times3) + \\hat{k}(-1\\times1 - 2\\times3) = -4\\hat{i} - 2\\hat{j} - 7\\hat{k}$",
    "",
    "**b)** $\\vec{b} \\times \\vec{a} = -\\vec{a} \\times \\vec{b}$ ✓",
    "",
    "**c)** $\\vec{a} \\times \\vec{a} = \\vec{0}$ ✓",
    "",
    "### Exercise 2: Cross Product with Unit Vectors",
    "",
    "**a)** $\\hat{i} \\times \\hat{i} = \\vec{0}$, $\\hat{i} \\times \\hat{j} = \\hat{k}$, $\\hat{i} \\times \\hat{k} = -\\hat{j}$",
    "$\\hat{j} \\times \\hat{i} = -\\hat{k}$, $\\hat{j} \\times \\hat{j} = \\vec{0}$, $\\hat{j} \\times \\hat{k} = \\hat{i}$",
    "$\\hat{k} \\times \\hat{i} = \\hat{j}$, $\\hat{k} \\times \\hat{j} = -\\hat{i}$, $\\hat{k} \\times \\hat{k} = \\vec{0}$",
    "",
    "**b)** $\\vec{a} \\times \\vec{b} = (a_y b_z - a_z b_y)\\hat{i} + (a_z b_x - a_x b_z)\\hat{j} + (a_x b_y - a_y b_x)\\hat{k}$",
    "",
    "**c)** Along axes: $\\hat{i} \\times \\hat{j} = \\hat{k}$, etc.",
    "",
    "### Exercise 3: Properties of Cross Product",
    "",
    "**a)** $\\vec{a} \\times \\vec{b} = -\\vec{b} \\times \\vec{a}$ ✓",
    "",
    "**b)** $\\vec{a} \\times (\\vec{b} + \\vec{c}) = \\vec{a} \\times \\vec{b} + \\vec{a} \\times \\vec{c}$ ✓",
    "",
    "**c)** $(k\\vec{a}) \\times \\vec{b} = k(\\vec{a} \\times \\vec{b})$ ✓",
    "",
    "**d)** $\\vec{a} \\times \\vec{0} = \\vec{0}$ ✓",
    "",
    "**e)** $\\vec{a} \\times (-\\vec{b}) = -(\\vec{a} \\times \\vec{b})$ ✓",
    "",
    "**f)** No: (a×b)×c ≠ a×(b×c) in general",
    "",
    "### Exercise 4: Magnitude and Direction of Cross Product",
    "",
    "**a)** $||\\vec{a} \\times \\vec{b}|| = \\sqrt{(a_y b_z - a_z b_y)^2 + (a_z b_x - a_x b_z)^2 + (a_x b_y - a_y b_x)^2}$",
    "",
    "**b)** $||\\vec{a} \\times \\vec{b}|| = ||\\vec{a}|| \\cdot ||\\vec{b}|| \\cdot |\\sin\\theta|$ ✓",
    "",
    "**c)** Maximum when θ = 90°, minimum when θ = 0° or 180°",
    "",
    "**d)** Right-hand rule: fingers curl from a to b, thumb points in direction of a×b",
    "",
    "**e)** $\\frac{\\vec{a} \\times \\vec{b}}{||\\vec{a} \\times \\vec{b}||}$",
    "",
    "### Exercise 5: Area of Parallelogram and Triangle",
    "",
    "**a)** Area = ||\\begin{pmatrix} 3 \\\\ 0 \\\\ 0 \\end{pmatrix} \\times \\begin{pmatrix} 0 \\\\ 4 \\\\ 0 \\end{pmatrix}|| = ||\\begin{pmatrix} 0 \\\\ 0 \\\\ 12 \\end{pmatrix}|| = 12$",
    "",
    "**b)** Vectors AB = $\\begin{pmatrix} -1 \\\\ 1 \\\\ 0 \\end{pmatrix}$, AC = $\\begin{pmatrix} -1 \\\\ 0 \\\\ 1 \\end{pmatrix}$, Area = (1/2)||AB × AC|| = (1/2)||\\begin{pmatrix} 1 \\\\ -1 \\\\ 1 \\end{pmatrix}|| = (1/2)√3$",
    "",
    "**c)** Area = ||\\vec{u} \\times \\vec{v}|| = ||\\begin{pmatrix} 2 \\\\ 1 \\\\ 3 \\end{pmatrix} \\times \\begin{pmatrix} 1 \\\\ 2 \\\\ 1 \\end{pmatrix}|| = ||\\begin{pmatrix} 1-6 \\\\ 2-3 \\\\ 4-2 \\end{pmatrix}|| = ||\\begin{pmatrix} -5 \\\\ -1 \\\\ 2 \\end{pmatrix}|| = √30$",
    "",
    "**d)** Triangle area = (1/2) × base × height = (1/2) × ||a|| × ||b|| × |sinθ| = (1/2)||a × b|| ✓",
    "",
    "### Exercise 6: Vector Triple Product",
    "",
    "**a)** $(\\vec{a} \\times \\vec{b}) \\times \\vec{c} = \\begin{pmatrix} 0 \\\\ 0 \\\\ 1 \\end{pmatrix} \\times \\begin{pmatrix} 0 \\\\ 0 \\\\ 1 \\end{pmatrix} = \\vec{0}$",
    "",
    "**b)** $\\vec{a} \\times (\\vec{b} \\times \\vec{c}) = (\\vec{a} \\cdot \\vec{c})\\vec{b} - (\\vec{a} \\cdot \\vec{b})\\vec{c}$ ✓",
    "",
    "**c)** $(\\vec{a} \\times \\vec{b}) \\times \\vec{c} = (\\vec{a} \\cdot \\vec{c})\\vec{b} - (\\vec{b} \\cdot \\vec{c})\\vec{a}$ ✓",
    "",
    "**d)** $(\\vec{a} \\times \\vec{b}) \\cdot \\vec{c} = \\begin{vmatrix} a_x & a_y & a_z \\\\ b_x & b_y & b_z \\\\ c_x & c_y & c_z \\end{vmatrix}$",
    "",
    "### Exercise 7: Applications in Physics",
    "",
    "**a)** Torque = $\\vec{r} \\times \\vec{F} = \\begin{pmatrix} 2 \\\\ 0 \\\\ 0 \\end{pmatrix} \\times \\begin{pmatrix} 0 \\\\ 10 \\\\ 0 \\end{pmatrix} = \\begin{pmatrix} 0 \\\\ 0 \\\\ 20 \\end{pmatrix}$ Nm",
